{"tid":2181316,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"放走阿蘇？巴塞要賠1200萬鎊","createTime":"2020-08-30T13:37:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-31T05:52:56.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e9f6660af6d0b6bdd3f8b458c0d7a06880d97638","tid":2181316,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T13:37:03.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports】西媒指出，巴塞隆拿如要蘇亞雷斯今夏離隊，需向後者賠償1200萬鎊。<br />\n<br />\n有傳巴塞隆拿新任教練朗奴高文曾親自致電蘇亞雷斯（Luis Suarez），並告知他「不在球會的計劃當中」。此刻雖然未有確切消息指阿蘇會離隊，而他周日亦有回到巴塞進行新冠病毒檢測，不過西班牙的傳媒消息似乎一面倒傾向認為他非走不可，更指巴塞有必要為終止雙方合約付出賠償，金額約為1200萬鎊。<br />\n<br />\n如巴塞最終向阿蘇作出賠償，這名33歲烏拉圭前鋒就可免費轉會，據稱現時已有5間球會對阿蘇有興趣。<br />\n<br />\n阿蘇早前在個人社交網絡instagram 中首度就事件開腔回應：「最近有些人冒我之名，對我的未來說三道四，這些人與我已多年沒有往來。在適合的時候，我會好好解釋自己的事情。」<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"cbb19f1bd5b5536306e60018caa9f5548a0e67cb","tid":2181316,"uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T13:37:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EgqLd98WAAAtRP_?format=jpg&amp;name=medium\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEgqLd98WAAAtRP_%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dmedium&h=e8a57a0b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b33e2126100ce06d6571db20c0744003ed9d8a42","tid":2181316,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T13:39:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3daab16bea1ad30bbf306286ed8c1c62a2b7a0c5","tid":2181316,"uid":310700,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T13:40:51.000Z","msg":"DLLMCH<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">你含撚啦高文</span></span></strong></span><br />\n一黎就搞散成team"},{"pid":"a1a33725a3f9da3d72172af780d35678faaabb47","tid":2181316,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cbb19f1bd5b5536306e60018caa9f5548a0e67cb","tid":2181316,"uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T13:37:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EgqLd98WAAAt